Investors will not be able to buy SSE Securities under the following circumstances: 
							a) the SSE Securities cease to be a constituent stock of the relevant indices; 
							b) the SSE Securities are under risk alert board;
							c) the corresponding H share of the SSE Securities cease to be traded on SEHK;
							d) the Daily Quota Balance drops to zero or below;
							e) the Aggregate Quota Balance is less than Daily Quota.

Eligible applicant must:
be our i-banking customer(personal customer);
be an individual applicant;
have a valid securities trading account (yellow form application);
Some companies may accept IPO applications from non Hong Kong residents. Please refer to respective Prospectus for details.
